details: Manufacturer of standard and custom agricultural equipment, specifically irrigation enhancers. Features neutralization of negative effects of salinity and other contaminants; reduction of plant stress; and magneto-hydrodynamic frequency driven using the moving fluid energy. Specifications include 20 to 3500 gpm flow rates, 60 to 87 in. lengths, 16 to 36 in. widths, and 13-1/4 to 30 in. heights. Made from 304 stainless steel housing and wetted components. Other products offered are separators and filters. Suitable for farms, nurseries, golf courses, parks, and landscapes.
